due to insufficient evidence.

00:03:04.800 --> 00:03:05.710
This time, we must

00:03:05.710 --> 00:03:07.970
hold him accountable for what he's done.

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:15.520
Okay.

00:03:18.329 --> 00:03:21.310
I'm only doing this
because you have sufficient evidence.

00:03:21.310 --> 00:03:22.840
I hereby authorize you

00:03:23.190 --> 00:03:25.450
to rejoin the investigation of this case

00:03:26.190 --> 00:03:28.750
and apprehend Gu Sinian
as soon as possible.

00:03:31.360 --> 00:03:32.590
-Yes, sir!
-Yes, sir!

00:03:35.440 --> 00:03:36.570
Come on, take a look.

00:03:36.760 --> 00:03:38.000
Have you seen this person before?

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:38.920
No, I haven't.

00:03:48.430 --> 00:03:49.220
Hello,

00:03:49.280 --> 00:03:50.740
have you seen this person?

00:03:51.360 --> 00:03:52.000
No.

00:03:54.190 --> 00:03:55.190
Hello, excuse me.

00:03:55.240 --> 00:03:56.700
Have you seen this person?

00:04:16.769 --> 00:04:19.810
[Yuanyu Pawnshop]

00:04:25.440 --> 00:04:28.500
[Open]

00:04:28.500 --> 00:04:28.850
Come on,

00:04:28.850 --> 00:04:30.310
let's go inside and check.

00:04:54.159 --> 00:04:55.090
Someone's here!

00:05:05.390 --> 00:05:06.350
The body is still warm.

00:05:06.350 --> 00:05:07.610
He's just been killed.

00:06:13.220 --> 00:06:14.130
Gu Sinian.

00:06:15.040 --> 00:06:15.770
Stop hiding.

00:06:16.690 --> 00:06:17.560
Come out now!

00:06:58.680 --> 00:06:59.310
Gu Sinian,

00:06:59.659 --> 00:07:00.650
we've surrounded this place completely!

00:07:00.650 --> 00:07:01.650
You can't escape!

00:07:03.700 --> 00:07:05.530
There's no point in catching me!

00:07:07.300 --> 00:07:09.010
I have the film now!

00:07:21.340 --> 00:07:23.190
If I destroy this film...

00:07:24.510 --> 00:07:27.310
you won't be able to convict me
even if you catch me!

00:07:30.360 --> 00:07:32.690
There are many people like me in Shanghai!

00:07:34.630 --> 00:07:36.120
Go catch them instead!

00:07:43.070 --> 00:07:44.360
Save

00:07:45.750 --> 00:07:47.390
that speech for prison.

00:07:56.570 --> 00:07:57.450
Gu Sinian!

00:07:59.070 --> 00:08:00.200
Come out, Gu Sinian!

00:08:01.000 --> 00:08:01.630
Guan Cen!

00:08:02.310 --> 00:08:03.520
You almost shot me!

00:08:04.040 --> 00:08:05.310
Don't be so impatient!

00:08:07.190 --> 00:08:08.520
Hear me out!

00:08:09.570 --> 00:08:11.630
The two of us can actually cooperate!

00:08:11.950 --> 00:08:13.950
You know how important this film is!

00:08:14.500 --> 00:08:16.630
It can bring you both fame and fortune,

00:08:16.950 --> 00:08:18.810
and it can also advance my career!

00:08:18.820 --> 00:08:19.880
If you're willing,

00:08:20.350 --> 00:08:22.150
I can give you the film right now!

00:08:22.580 --> 00:08:23.300
Gu Sinian,

00:08:24.070 --> 00:08:26.270
you spent years collecting this stuff,

00:08:26.480 --> 00:08:28.410
and you'd give it to me that easily?

00:08:28.750 --> 00:08:30.610
Stop playing games! Come out now!

00:08:39.669 --> 00:08:41.700
Inspector Guan, you certainly like to
promote yourself

00:08:41.700 --> 00:08:44.500
as someone who doesn't care about
fame or fortune!

00:08:45.120 --> 00:08:47.120
Stop pretending to be so noble here!

00:08:47.720 --> 00:08:48.510
Guan Cen!

00:08:56.720 --> 00:08:59.240
Don't you know
how you became an inspector?

00:09:00.360 --> 00:09:02.090
Was it because of your ability?

00:09:02.960 --> 00:09:04.720
Wasn't it
because of that idiot Huo Zhongji

00:09:04.720 --> 00:09:06.050
and his support for you?

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:08.960
And Lu Yizhen!

00:09:14.640 --> 00:09:17.840
You used the Nanyang Chamber of Commerce's
influence...

00:09:17.980 --> 00:09:19.380
to join the police force!

00:09:20.550 --> 00:09:21.750
You're a young woman!

00:09:22.860 --> 00:09:25.320
What qualifies you to be
in the police force?

00:09:26.600 --> 00:09:28.630
If Guan Cen hadn't helped you...

00:09:29.810 --> 00:09:31.600
you'd still be working under Zhu Yunsong,

00:09:31.600 --> 00:09:33.460
filing documents, wouldn't you?

00:09:38.150 --> 00:09:40.390
You enjoy
the Nanyang Chamber of Commerce's benefits

00:09:40.390 --> 00:09:42.050
yet come here to play the hero!

00:09:42.550 --> 00:09:44.210
I'm even embarrassed for you!

00:09:45.960 --> 00:09:46.630
Gu Sinian,

00:09:47.110 --> 00:09:48.270
this is all you're good at—

00:09:48.270 --> 00:09:49.390
slinging mud.

00:09:50.020 --> 00:09:51.820
Yizhen, don't let him get to you.

00:09:59.100 --> 00:09:59.930
What?

00:10:00.150 --> 00:10:01.060
Struck a nerve?

00:10:01.080 --> 00:10:02.340
You're angry now, huh?

00:10:55.120 --> 00:10:55.580
Yizhen,

00:10:56.190 --> 00:10:57.120
are you alright?

00:10:57.770 --> 00:10:58.450
I'm fine.

00:10:58.600 --> 00:10:59.460
What about you?

00:10:59.670 --> 00:11:00.440
I'm okay.

00:11:00.770 --> 00:11:02.050
I think I shot him.

00:11:06.360 --> 00:11:07.050
Guan Cen!

00:11:08.790 --> 00:11:10.990
Don't you want to see your sister again?

00:11:12.910 --> 00:11:13.670
Where is she?

00:11:14.080 --> 00:11:15.120
Your sister is still waiting

00:11:15.120 --> 00:11:16.670
for you to save her!

00:11:17.280 --> 00:11:19.010
You haven't seen her for years!

00:11:19.570 --> 00:11:22.100
Don't you want to know
what she looks like now?

00:11:22.970 --> 00:11:25.370
Does she still remember you
as her brother?

00:11:25.980 --> 00:11:27.640
Has she gotten married by now?

00:11:28.360 --> 00:11:29.750
What's her child like?

00:11:29.750 --> 00:11:31.270
Don't you want to know all of that?

00:11:31.270 --> 00:11:32.480
I can tell you!

00:11:34.240 --> 00:11:35.840
That's just talk. Prove it.

00:11:36.360 --> 00:11:38.360
Guan Jingning has a sachet

00:11:38.980 --> 00:11:40.910
with lotus flowers embroidered on it,

00:11:40.910 --> 00:11:41.630
right?

00:11:47.310 --> 00:11:48.040
Where is she?

00:11:50.390 --> 00:11:51.450
Before I came here,

00:11:51.480 --> 00:11:54.010
I arranged for Tang Jiahao
to take care of her.

00:11:54.430 --> 00:11:55.550
If you want,

00:11:56.150 --> 00:11:57.390
I can take you to her!

00:11:57.990 --> 00:11:59.390
You still don't trust me?

00:11:59.960 --> 00:12:01.390
I'll give you my gun now.

00:12:03.910 --> 00:12:05.440
Isn't that sincere enough?

00:12:12.270 --> 00:12:13.530
Where's the evidence?

00:12:13.720 --> 00:12:15.480
Then let me show you something.

00:12:16.150 --> 00:12:17.880
Open your eyes and look at this.

00:12:22.750 --> 00:12:23.880
Do you recognize it?

00:12:27.910 --> 00:12:28.970
I'm coming out now!

00:12:29.610 --> 00:12:30.550
Don't shoot!

00:12:36.320 --> 00:12:36.910
Come out.

00:12:42.630 --> 00:12:43.480
Is this it?

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:47.880
Guan Cen.

00:12:49.200 --> 00:12:50.550
We're old friends.

00:12:51.110 --> 00:12:52.510
There's no need for this.

00:12:52.800 --> 00:12:55.130
Put down your gun,
and I'll take you to her.

00:13:03.280 --> 00:13:04.080
Lu Yizhen.

00:13:04.500 --> 00:13:06.270
You already shot me.

00:13:08.240 --> 00:13:10.970
You don't want him to lose
his last chance, do you?

00:13:15.650 --> 00:13:16.290
Guan Cen.

00:13:17.510 --> 00:13:19.710
Don't forget how he deceived me before.

00:13:19.840 --> 00:13:22.040
He could be fooling you the same way now.

00:13:23.880 --> 00:13:24.590
Guan Cen.

00:13:26.140 --> 00:13:28.210
The priority now isn't to catch me.

00:13:29.120 --> 00:13:30.520
It's to save your sister.

00:13:31.150 --> 00:13:32.720
Every minute you waste here

00:13:32.720 --> 00:13:34.600
is another minute of uncertainty
over there.

00:13:34.600 --> 00:13:36.720
This might really be your last chance.

00:13:36.720 --> 00:13:37.980
Can you afford to wait?

00:13:51.210 --> 00:13:51.870
Yizhen.

00:14:24.160 --> 00:14:25.090
Are you alright?

00:14:25.180 --> 00:14:26.040
How do you feel?

00:14:32.120 --> 00:14:32.860
Let me see.

00:14:36.500 --> 00:14:37.020
Take him away!

00:14:37.020 --> 00:14:38.220
-Yes, sir!
-Yes, sir!

00:14:41.360 --> 00:14:42.820
We'll talk at the station.

00:14:43.030 --> 00:14:43.910
Careful.

00:14:46.680 --> 00:14:47.210
Let's go.

00:15:12.980 --> 00:15:15.910
You arranged for Tang Jiahao
to kill Ghost in prison.

00:15:19.550 --> 00:15:20.350
That's right.

00:15:21.270 --> 00:15:22.800
Who else could it have been?

00:15:23.240 --> 00:15:25.770
Tang Jiahao wiped out
the entire Zhuo family—

00:15:26.390 --> 00:15:28.250
you ordered that too, didn't you?

00:15:28.960 --> 00:15:30.510
I wouldn't say that.

00:15:30.960 --> 00:15:31.960
Let's just say...

00:15:33.790 --> 00:15:35.200
he's very good...

00:15:36.600 --> 00:15:38.320
at anticipating my wishes.

00:15:39.010 --> 00:15:40.530
You were also the one

00:15:41.750 --> 00:15:44.410
who leaked information
about Huang Kaiyuan...

00:15:45.030 --> 00:15:46.630
to Tang Jiahao, weren't you?

00:15:46.910 --> 00:15:48.360
Huang Kaiyuan...

00:15:55.320 --> 00:15:58.000
If you two hadn't thought of
sending me to him...

00:16:00.120 --> 00:16:02.550
I really wouldn't have known where he was.

00:16:03.130 --> 00:16:05.290
Maybe he really could've escaped.

00:16:06.730 --> 00:16:07.850
So tell me—

00:16:08.920 --> 00:16:10.060
was that heaven's help,

00:16:10.060 --> 00:16:11.850
or help from you two?

00:16:20.510 --> 00:16:21.910
Where is Tang Jiahao now?

00:16:22.360 --> 00:16:22.870
What?

00:16:23.960 --> 00:16:26.160
I'm asking you where Tang Jiahao is now.

00:16:26.910 --> 00:16:28.120
I don't know either.

00:16:30.050 --> 00:16:31.250
However...

00:16:32.380 --> 00:16:34.440
he'll probably come looking for you.

00:16:35.080 --> 00:16:36.740
No matter where he escapes to,

00:16:36.920 --> 00:16:38.590
we will bring him to justice,

00:16:39.820 --> 00:16:42.220
and he will face punishment alongside you.

00:16:44.300 --> 00:16:45.990
He probably won't run away.

00:16:46.790 --> 00:16:48.200
After dealing with him for so many years,

00:16:48.200 --> 00:16:49.860
don't you understand him yet?

00:16:50.320 --> 00:16:52.390
With you escapees still here,

00:16:53.390 --> 00:16:55.120
how could he possibly run away?

00:16:59.120 --> 00:17:00.150
We already have

00:17:00.710 --> 00:17:02.640
all those films in our possession.

00:17:03.550 --> 00:17:06.069
Capturing you is
only the beginning, Gu Sinian.

00:17:06.069 --> 00:17:08.000
We won't spare anyone backing you.

00:17:16.920 --> 00:17:18.880
Await your judgment, Dr. Gu.

00:17:21.880 --> 00:17:22.790
Eat it quickly.

00:17:23.460 --> 00:17:25.319
You'll never get to have it again.

00:17:35.370 --> 00:17:37.440
We have evidence of Gu Sinian's crimes.

00:17:37.440 --> 00:17:39.440
It won't be difficult to convict him.

00:17:39.440 --> 00:17:41.200
How's the processing
of the films coming along?

00:17:41.200 --> 00:17:42.590
According to him, the films contain

00:17:42.590 --> 00:17:44.000
records of the business dealings
of the organization behind him.

00:17:44.000 --> 00:17:44.730
Is that true?

00:17:45.960 --> 00:17:47.000
The records show

00:17:47.270 --> 00:17:49.460
all of Skylark Company's transactions

00:17:49.460 --> 00:17:51.500
and client lists over the years.

00:17:53.200 --> 00:17:54.460
Surprising, isn't it?

00:17:54.510 --> 00:17:55.720
They documented

00:17:55.750 --> 00:17:57.210
all their crimes this way.

00:17:57.270 --> 00:17:58.730
So can we make arrests now?

00:17:59.260 --> 00:17:59.940
Not yet.

00:18:00.630 --> 00:18:02.100
The films are severely damaged,

00:18:02.100 --> 00:18:03.960
and the records aren't complete.

00:18:05.000 --> 00:18:05.530
However,

00:18:06.270 --> 00:18:07.880
we can follow these records

00:18:08.440 --> 00:18:10.190
to locate the people from Skylark Company

00:18:10.190 --> 00:18:11.790
and round them all up at once.

00:18:13.100 --> 00:18:15.030
I wonder if we can find Tang Jiahao.

00:18:15.970 --> 00:18:17.770
That's the second piece of news.

00:18:18.310 --> 00:18:20.680
I've already sent people out
to search for him.

00:18:20.680 --> 00:18:22.410
We should hear something soon.

00:18:27.520 --> 00:18:28.780
And the third thing...

00:18:30.730 --> 00:18:32.190
It's regarding Jingning.

00:18:33.550 --> 00:18:34.880
You have news about her?

00:18:36.000 --> 00:18:37.640
I remember you mentioned before

00:18:37.640 --> 00:18:39.240
that when Mr. Jin met with Tang Jiahao,

00:18:39.240 --> 00:18:41.300
they talked about a girl who escaped.

00:18:41.480 --> 00:18:42.280
That's right.

00:18:43.030 --> 00:18:44.360
Mr. Jin said at the time,

00:18:45.060 --> 00:18:47.120
"She fell down. What else could I do?"

00:18:47.830 --> 00:18:49.880
It must be that after the factory
burned down,

00:18:49.880 --> 00:18:52.130
Tang Jiahao needed to
move Jingning quickly,

00:18:52.130 --> 00:18:53.590
so he left her with Mr. Jin.

00:18:53.830 --> 00:18:55.640
Using the abandoned factory as the center,

00:18:55.640 --> 00:18:58.040
I intend to search every potential site...

00:18:58.960 --> 00:19:01.310
within a five‑li radius
where a person could have fallen.

00:19:01.310 --> 00:19:03.440
Because if the place were easy to find,

00:19:03.750 --> 00:19:05.640
