00:19:05.640 --> 00:19:06.860
when she fell back then.

00:19:06.860 --> 00:19:08.400
But Tang Jiahao and his people didn't.

00:19:08.400 --> 00:19:09.810
So I suspect the place she fell

00:19:09.810 --> 00:19:11.000
might have been a steep slope

00:19:11.000 --> 00:19:11.860
or even a cliff.

00:19:13.480 --> 00:19:14.110
Here.

00:19:14.720 --> 00:19:15.200
Here.

00:19:15.790 --> 00:19:16.240
Here.

00:19:16.400 --> 00:19:16.830
And...

00:19:17.440 --> 00:19:18.160
here.

00:19:19.000 --> 00:19:20.070
These villages

00:19:20.270 --> 00:19:21.830
