00:19:21.830 --> 00:19:23.850
Villagers nearby often go up
into the mountains

00:19:23.850 --> 00:19:25.050
to cut grass and hunt.

00:19:25.710 --> 00:19:27.480
So it's possible someone might've run into

00:19:27.480 --> 00:19:28.880
Jingning after she fell.

00:19:29.310 --> 00:19:30.110
Of course...

00:19:31.030 --> 00:19:32.830
