00:19:32.830 --> 00:19:35.430
her remains would also be
in one of these areas.

00:19:35.850 --> 00:19:36.790
Even if there's only a glimmer of hope,

00:19:36.790 --> 00:19:38.590
I must continue investigating.

00:19:40.350 --> 00:19:42.680
That's exactly
what I've been waiting to hear.

00:19:42.680 --> 00:19:44.120
I've already sent
the Intelligence Department

00:19:44.120 --> 00:19:45.780
